      • and

        public Goal and(Goal goal)
        Returns an "AND" GoalI. The GoalI "AND" succeeds if both of the Goals 'this' and the parameter 'goal' succeed. The GoalI "AND" fails if at least one of the Goals 'this' or the parameter 'goal' fail.
        Parameters:
        goal - the other GoalI which is part of the new "AND" GoalI.
        Returns:
        solver.and(this, goal)
